Grantham, Mayo, Van Otterloo & Co. LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 8:37 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Grantham, Mayo, Van Otterloo & Co. LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Grantham, Mayo, Van Otterloo & Co. LLC is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm provides its services to high net worth individuals, investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, state or municipal government entities, and other investment advisers. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, balanced and multi- portfolios. The firm also launches and manages equity, fixed income, balanced mutual funds, and hedge funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm also invests in commodities and currencies markets. It invests in derivatives...
Grantham, Mayo, Van Otterloo & Co. LLC is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm provides its services to high net worth individuals, investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, state or municipal government entities, and other investment advisers. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, balanced and multi- portfolios. The firm also launches and manages equity, fixed income, balanced mutual funds, and hedge funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm also invests in commodities and currencies markets. It invests in derivatives as well. For the equity portion of its portfolio, the firm typically makes its investments in value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. For the fixed income portfion of its portfolio, it invests in diversified portfolio of investments including sovereign and quasi-sovereign debt instruments, asset-backed securities, government bonds, and U.S. and non-U.S. fixed income securities. It employs absolute return and long/short strategies to make its investment. The firm employs fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Citigroup Indices, Barclays Indices, J.P. Morgan Indices, MSCI Indices, and S&P Indices. The firm invests in natural resources sector. It conducts in-house research to make its investments. Grantham, Mayo, Van Otterloo & Co. was founded in 1977 and is based in Boston, Massachusetts with an additional offices in Berkeley, California and San Francisco, California.
Detailed Description


40 Rowes WharfBoston, MA 02110-3340United StatesFounded in 1977



