Grantham, Mayo, Van Otterloo & Co. LLC Key Developments

GMO Presents at Morningstar Investment Conference Chicago 2017, Apr-27-2017 09:10 AM
Apr 4 17
GMO Presents at Morningstar Investment Conference Chicago 2017, Apr-27-2017 09:10 AM. Venue: Hyatt Regency McCormick Place, 2233 South Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. Drive, Chicago, IL 60616, Illinois, United States. Speakers: Catherine LeGraw.


Grantham, Mayo, Van Otterloo & Co. LLC Announces Executive Changes, Effective February 13, 2017
Jan 23 17
Grantham, Mayo, Van Otterloo & Co. LLC announced that Scott Hayward, former CEO of Quantitative Management Associates LLC (QMA), will take the helm of GMO as CEO effective February 13, 2017, replacing Peg McGetrick, current CEO on an interim basis, who will remain a Director of the firm. Hayward spent 13 years at QMA, including 11 as CEO. He previously held executive positions at Jennison Associates and JPMorgan. McGetrick also announced the hiring of Andy Martin from Cambridge Associates (CA) to fill a newly created role, Head of Investment Teams.
Martin spent 10 years with CA, most recently as Managing Director in the non-profit practice and Global Head of Hedge Fund Research.


Grantham Mayo Van Otterloo & Co Lays Off 10% of Workforce
Jun 17 16
Grantham Mayo Van Otterloo & Co has laid off approximately 10% of its 650 employees worldwide. Grantham Mayo Van Otterloo & Co layoffs, including how many Boston-based personnel are affected. The firm, which was founded by the acclaimed British investor Jeremy Grantham, also has offices in Berkeley, California; London; Amsterdam; Sydney; and Singapore.


